{"tid":1939854,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（揀科撚）興趣 VS 前景/錢途","createTime":"2020-03-23T11:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T15:01:16.000Z","uid":146917,"like":136,"dislike":123,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"bb713bc2d3793999bde4c8a6ec322ea746f545a4","tid":1939854,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:29:20.000Z","msg":"幫下DSE雞 睇下過來人點揀<br />\n<br />\n我先 唔理興趣 揀錢行先<br />\n因為我個人比較現實 興趣唔可以當飯食<br />\n當我有錢就會有興趣<br />\n<br />\n有人後悔揀興趣<br />\n有人後悔冇跟自己興趣讀得好辛苦<br />\n大家再黎過又會點揀？<br />\n順手可以撚發下dse同學<br />\n<br />\n興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前景/錢途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7299f7f20d2ee59ec8273a04bd9793ebb7a54392","tid":1939854,"uid":76931,"like":37,"dislike":6,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:38:12.000Z","msg":"錢途<br />\n有到錢隨時可以讀返master 興趣"},{"pid":"29050a9e287351743f2cb8c07a3aaf14558da979","tid":1939854,"uid":88374,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:39:28.000Z","msg":"求鳩其啦<br />\n自己邊範叻咪揀邊範"},{"pid":"2b2b0fd60030ace67d6838528e03f9522003f21e","tid":1939854,"uid":208823,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"一定係讀bba 未來企業家 賺大錢 體驗贏嘅感覺<br />\n（最後比人管理）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74a5b4081c237ccacf87ee8e84e6bc0ce3fc74a","tid":1939854,"uid":141401,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:54:12.000Z","msg":"興趣 <br />\n之前讀Civil一啲都唔鐘意 純粹為錢途 成日都唔好<br />\n而家轉左讀有興趣既Aviation日日上堂都好興奮 雖然而家航空真心無咩前景"},{"pid":"748e5496c8fe44325aff1d37e7361cb606135b9c","tid":1939854,"uid":322685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:54:47.000Z","msg":"興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無諗過前景"},{"pid":"52884d7dfeedc60626287ffca6d9428f840b30b2","tid":1939854,"uid":228143,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"冇興趣你讀理科包你畢唔到業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08207d5fd6e344c9cbf0f0f3e7c17c10dbc3f359","tid":1939854,"uid":131245,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"bb713bc2d3793999bde4c8a6ec322ea746f545a4","tid":1939854,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:29:20.000Z","msg":"幫下DSE雞 睇下過來人點揀<br />\n<br />\n我先 唔理興趣 揀錢行先<br />\n因為我個人比較現實 興趣唔可以當飯食<br />\n當我有錢就會有興趣<br />\n<br />\n有人後悔揀興趣<br />\n有人後悔冇跟自己興趣讀得好辛苦<br />\n大家再黎過又會點揀？<br />\n順手可以撚發下dse同學<br />\n<br />\n興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前景/錢途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T12:02:50.000Z","msg":"睇自己咩境環，人人都唔同。<br />\n<br />\n你根本唔使為錢煩，讀啲自己鍾意嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n如果要出嚟搵食，就讀啲大路啲嘅嘢；不過就算要搵食，揀興趣都無乜所謂，因為有興趣自然做得好，做得好自然會有錢。<br />\n<br />\n到最後揀乜科都無乜所謂，你讀文學啫，無人會阻你去了解量子物理學架"},{"pid":"d3d0a7d1d447f3ad2246f9b1c2b63d1f4ad211ab","tid":1939854,"uid":146917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52884d7dfeedc60626287ffca6d9428f840b30b2","tid":1939854,"uid":228143,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"冇興趣你讀理科包你畢唔到業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T12:04:39.000Z","msg":"畢到<br />\n利申 我"},{"pid":"b643f5c93b64fba8e4fef7b8579998fa0641681b","tid":1939854,"uid":81273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T12:04:58.000Z","msg":"忠告：睇科名睇連登睇新聞係唔會知係咪真係興趣"},{"pid":"7e95f88128d5e81c46380a8ba4f7582d2a9f394b","tid":1939854,"uid":199479,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T12:05:07.000Z","msg":"我嘅興趣係錢 所以點都揀搵食科"},{"pid":"4e20235a08ef071a5811cf642cab865b2919e84d","tid":1939854,"uid":131245,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"52884d7dfeedc60626287ffca6d9428f840b