/><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌， <br />\n就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。 <br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <br />\n簡直是公司主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"9b9fc6733d54ff826b8e9e9d229d3e2b4b0b455a","tid":1939854,"uid":340004,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T12:19:31.000Z","msg":"香港地，冇牌考嘅科都係乞架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />科科都乞咁我梗係揀有興趣嘅讀，起碼gpa會靚仔啲"},{"pid":"2c7129af980c39694e45b278518d66c96119c304","tid":1939854,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3af662c197ea58fd96e1cc3fd126425ac6510f4","tid":1939854,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d3d0a7d1d447f3ad2246f9b1c2b63d1f4ad211ab","tid":1939854,"uid":146917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52884d7dfeedc60626287ffca6d9428f840b30b2","tid":1939854,"uid":228143,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"冇興趣你讀理科包你畢唔到業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T12:04:39.000Z","msg":"畢到<br />\n利申 我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T12:07:25.000Z","msg":"咩系"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T12:20:13.000Z","msg":"CS"},{"pid":"a497a41175a584b5af3c78d8cad70c1912a4e021","tid":1939854,"uid":167464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T12:25:02.000Z","msg":"讀緊有興趣但錢途一般般嘅科，雖然知道讀完啲嘢應該以後用唔著，但讀嘅嘢我覺得好有趣，次次有新嘢學都好興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但畢業之後應該會幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13985b421f9222390b537835fec3caabab31587e","tid":1939854,"uid":199479,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"