意科學揀醫療類或者你鍾意數理揀工程咁。"},{"pid":"4e050ff72be299fb7cbadbbbdd4e58c3442c69d3","tid":1939854,"uid":201890,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bb713bc2d3793999bde4c8a6ec322ea746f545a4","tid":1939854,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:29:20.000Z","msg":"幫下DSE雞 睇下過來人點揀<br />\n<br />\n我先 唔理興趣 揀錢行先<br />\n因為我個人比較現實 興趣唔可以當飯食<br />\n當我有錢就會有興趣<br />\n<br />\n有人後悔揀興趣<br />\n有人後悔冇跟自己興趣讀得好辛苦<br />\n大家再黎過又會點揀？<br />\n順手可以撚發下dse同學<br />\n<br />\n興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前景/錢途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T15:29:36.000Z","msg":"一句講曬 <br />\n<br />\n有父幹-興趣<br />\n冇父幹-你都係揀返搵食科算啦7頭，驚你未畢業已經餓死佐。"},{"pid":"42e6eafda8406f212866bc0b977cfdaa2ad75ad0","tid":1939854,"uid":234362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e74a5b4081c237ccacf87ee8e84e6bc0ce3fc74a","tid":1939854,"uid":141401,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:54:12.000Z","msg":"興趣 <br />\n之前讀Civil一啲都唔鐘意 純粹為錢途 成日都唔好<br />\n而家轉左讀有興趣既Aviation日日上堂都好興奮 雖然而家航空真心無咩前景"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T15:38:53.000Z","msg":"Aviation 長遠黎睇其實會穩定發展，唔使擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1acea6a7d74bec2c5b5e373dc4a917b375f96f","tid":1939854,"uid":89240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:23:37.000Z","msg":"有能力：興趣，將興趣變搵錢<br />\n廢物：錢途，搵到錢再玩興趣"},{"pid":"473dcac4ee29779b84ffdb52d7dbbe2ac853bd04","tid":1939854,"uid":71068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:26:02.000Z","msg":"當年揀咗興趣 而家食緊屎"},{"pid":"e37544c408b587251d7599d9244a4bb2a9728d37","tid":1939854,"uid":273364,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:32:44.000Z","msg":"揀左專科 讀得辛苦 將來搵到錢再玩返興趣<br />\n到時出黎人工就係一般人double <br />\n但真係讀得辛苦"},{"pid":"59784ff888850892e506cdb7f277bcf003483e4e","tid":1939854,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci